      "title": "Janani wins gold at Indian Open National Para-Athletics Championship",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lankan para-athlete Janani Dananjana has clinched the gold medal at the 4th Indian Open National Para-Athletics Championship 2022 in Bangalore, India.",
        "She participated in Women\u2019s Long Jump T47, a classification for athletes with movement affected at a low to moderate degree in one arm or the absence of limbs.",
        "Dananjana secured the gold medal by jumping the best distance of 5.01 meters and 690 points."
      ],
